data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom home in Fontana! With just a touch of personalization, this exceptional 4-bedroom residence has the potential to become the home of your dreams. Let's explore the possibilities together!"    The master bedroom boasts a private bathroom and French doors leading to the backyard. This property is move-in ready, with direct garage access and laundry. The side yard offers potential for additional vehicle storage RV Parking.    This home boasts a fantastic backyard with mesmerizing mountain views, creating the perfect backdrop for entertaining. Meanwhile, the beautifully landscaped front yard offers exceptional curb appeal, setting the stage for your dream home."    Situated on a quiet street with minimal traffic, this home is walking distance to Randall Pepper Elementary (K-5), Harry S. Truman Middle School (6-8), and Fontana High (9-12).    Don't miss the chance to own this fantastic, turnkey home in Fontana. Contact us today for a viewing!
